Adding a lesson

1. Create a new lesson directory- for example lesson1
2. Create a phrases.txt file inside the new lesson directory- for example lesson1/phrases.txt
3. Inside the phrases.txt, put one english phrase per line
4. run python3 gen_data.py lesson_name (for example lesson3)
5. run python3 gen_html.py lesson_name (for example lesson3)
6. Update index.html with a new link by adding a new line like <a href="lesson1.html"><h2>Lesson 1<h2></a>
7. In Github Desktop, press commit in the bottom left, and Push origin at the top